23. AI WORKFLOW STRATEGY
IMPORTANT RULE
Never ask AI tools to:
"Build the entire portfolio at once."
That creates:
inconsistent design,
broken responsiveness,
corrupted architecture,
duplicated code,
and unstable animation systems.

CORRECT WORKFLOW
PHASE 01 — FOUNDATION
Generate:
colors
typography
buttons
cards
spacing
grid system
dark/light mode
ONLY.

PHASE 02 — STATIC LAYOUTS
Generate:
Hero
About
Experience
Projects
Contact
WITHOUT advanced animations.

PHASE 03 — RESPONSIVENESS
Generate:
tablet layouts
mobile layouts
typography scaling
spacing optimization

PHASE 04 — ANIMATION
Generate:
Framer Motion
GSAP
cinematic interactions
smooth scroll systems
ONLY after layout stabilization.

PHASE 05 — OPTIMIZATION
Finalize:
performance
accessibility
cleanup
consistency
responsiveness
animation polish

